WEBVTT

00:27.114 --> 00:29.507
[thunder crack]

00:36.036 --> 00:38.995
[ominous music]

00:39.039 --> 00:40.866
♪♪

01:17.207 --> 01:20.123
[water trickling]

01:24.736 --> 01:26.825
[thunder crack]

01:34.616 --> 01:37.140
[indistinct whispering]

01:43.233 --> 01:45.235
[thunder crack]

02:06.126 --> 02:09.085
[whispering continues]

02:23.273 --> 02:24.622
- Mummy!

02:24.666 --> 02:24.970
Mummy!

02:25.667 --> 02:27.582
Mummy! Mummy!

02:27.973 --> 02:30.454
- What's wrong, Philip?

02:30.585 --> 02:31.803
Another nightmare?

02:31.847 --> 02:35.111
- No! There's something
under the sheets.

02:35.155 --> 02:36.852
For real this time!

02:36.895 --> 02:37.200
Look!

02:38.245 --> 02:41.073
- Let's have a look
at it then.

02:43.554 --> 02:44.729
See?

02:45.991 --> 02:48.255
How many times
have I told you?

02:48.298 --> 02:51.519
It's just your imagination.

02:51.649 --> 02:53.216
Now go to sleep,
it's late.

02:53.260 --> 02:55.827
- No, don't go!

02:56.001 --> 02:57.873
- Hold on.

02:59.701 --> 03:02.704
My grandmother gave this to me
when I was a little girl.

03:02.747 --> 03:04.140
Now,

03:04.184 --> 03:05.750
every time you're scared,

03:05.794 --> 03:07.970
hold it,
say a little prayer,

03:08.013 --> 03:10.581
and everything
will go away.

03:10.625 --> 03:12.235
- Are you sure?

03:12.279 --> 03:15.412
- Absolutely.
Now go to sleep.

03:19.024 --> 03:20.200
One...

03:20.243 --> 03:20.461
Two...

03:21.592 --> 03:21.766
Three.

03:22.724 --> 03:23.594
[light switch clicks]

03:23.638 --> 03:25.292
Goodnight.

03:25.596 --> 03:27.859
[footsteps leaving]

03:29.861 --> 03:31.863
[door creaking closed]
[thunder cracks]

03:37.521 --> 03:39.262
[clock chimes sounding]

03:46.617 --> 03:48.880
[thunder cracks]

03:50.404 --> 03:52.449
[wind chimes rattling]

03:55.539 --> 03:58.368
[thunder cracks]
[wind howling]

04:05.245 --> 04:07.421
[eerie music swells]

04:07.464 --> 04:09.379
♪♪

04:10.206 --> 04:11.338
- Mummy!

04:11.381 --> 04:13.209
[breathing heavily]

04:13.253 --> 04:14.819
Mummy!

04:15.733 --> 04:18.910
Mummy! Mummy!

04:19.128 --> 04:20.216
Mummy!

04:20.260 --> 04:23.306
- Philip!
My love!

04:23.350 --> 04:25.352
- It's still here!

04:25.395 --> 04:25.439
- It's alright!

04:26.614 --> 04:29.138
- It's in the shadows!
- Shh...

04:29.269 --> 04:31.532
- It's still moving!

04:33.751 --> 04:36.145
It's going to Isidore!

04:36.188 --> 04:36.276
- There's nothing there.
- Mummy!

04:38.408 --> 04:39.279
Mummy!

04:39.322 --> 04:41.281
- We've woken her up.

04:41.324 --> 04:43.674
Go on, to bed.
- Mummy!

04:43.718 --> 04:45.981
- Coming, Isidore!

04:47.461 --> 04:50.768
Here she is!
You see? She's fine!

04:50.812 --> 04:53.118
- What's happening, Mummy?

04:53.162 --> 04:53.641
- Nothing. Philip just wanted
to say goodnight.

04:55.599 --> 04:56.731
Go on, to bed!

04:56.774 --> 04:58.298
- Can I sleep with you?

04:58.341 --> 05:00.387
- There it is!

05:00.604 --> 05:02.345
It's over there!

05:02.476 --> 05:04.869
- Philip,
that's enough now!

05:05.609 --> 05:07.350
Go on,
everyone in the big bed!

05:07.394 --> 05:08.656
- Yay!

05:08.699 --> 05:11.093
[screaming]

05:11.485 --> 05:13.400
- Isidore! Isidore!

05:14.401 --> 05:16.446
Isidore!

05:16.490 --> 05:16.751
[pounding on door]

05:22.626 --> 05:24.454
[distant crying]

05:29.285 --> 05:31.331
[eerie music swells]

05:31.374 --> 05:33.289
♪♪

05:47.521 --> 05:50.306
[crying continues]

06:15.200 --> 06:16.376
- Eight...

06:16.419 --> 06:18.029
Nine...

06:18.073 --> 06:18.378
Ten.

06:23.687 --> 06:26.908
Ready or not,
here I come!

06:28.692 --> 06:30.738
Are you cold?

06:31.042 --> 06:32.914
- No.

06:36.265 --> 06:39.181
Isidore's watching us
from heaven

06:39.224 --> 06:43.925
and she wants us to be happy,
doesn't she?

06:52.107 --> 06:56.720
I had a dream about her
two nights ago.

06:56.938 --> 07:00.071
She was holding Piggy
and waving at me.

07:00.115 --> 07:00.811
- Ah!

07:01.290 --> 07:02.900
[chuckling]

07:04.206 --> 07:06.426
- Have you found
anything new?

07:08.123 --> 07:09.646
Oh-ho!

07:10.517 --> 07:13.781
Michael the Archangel!

07:13.955 --> 07:16.392
A true warrior.

07:16.523 --> 07:19.090
Just like you.
[chuckles]

07:21.049 --> 07:23.138
- Poor Piggy.

07:24.226 --> 07:26.402
Who knows where he's gone.

07:26.446 --> 07:26.707
- He's with her!

07:31.538 --> 07:35.063
Did he beat this monster?

07:35.498 --> 07:39.546
- This wasn't just
any old monster.

07:39.589 --> 07:40.242
This was a truly
powerful monster.

07:44.725 --> 07:46.378
Now. Keep it.

07:46.422 --> 07:48.250
- Thank you!

07:48.380 --> 07:49.381
- Right...

07:52.167 --> 07:53.516
- You're right.

07:54.822 --> 07:57.912
He's up there,
keeping her company.

08:01.002 --> 08:03.308
- Mum?
- Mm-hmm.

08:03.526 --> 08:06.616
- I'm scared that bad thing
will come back.

08:06.660 --> 08:08.923
- It won't.

08:09.053 --> 08:11.142
I promise.

08:11.360 --> 08:13.144
- What are we
going to do now?

08:13.188 --> 08:14.581
I know.

08:14.624 --> 08:16.496
Let's pray!
Okay?

08:16.539 --> 08:18.715
- Yeah!
- Come on then!

08:24.416 --> 08:26.244
- Now sleep.

08:26.418 --> 08:28.246
Lights off?

08:31.685 --> 08:34.208
Sweet dreams, my love.

08:35.123 --> 08:36.777
One...

08:36.907 --> 08:38.518
Two...

08:38.866 --> 08:40.128
Three.

08:40.171 --> 08:41.956
[light switch clicks]

08:43.566 --> 08:45.350
- Our Father,

08:45.394 --> 08:47.570
who art in heaven,

08:47.614 --> 08:49.833
hallowed be thy name.

08:49.877 --> 08:51.661
Thy kingdom come,

08:51.705 --> 08:53.924
thy will be done,

08:53.968 --> 08:54.403
on earth
as it is in heaven.

08:57.101 --> 08:57.319
[dramatic orchestral music]

08:59.147 --> 09:00.975
♪♪

09:32.354 --> 09:36.663
[cellphone ringing]

09:41.145 --> 09:43.757
- Hi, honey!
How are you?

09:44.714 --> 09:46.629
I'm looking forward to later.

09:46.673 --> 09:48.500
How was your practice?

09:58.510 --> 10:01.949
- Give us this day
our daily bread,

10:01.992 --> 10:02.819
- and forgive us
our trespasses

10:04.473 --> 10:08.608
as we forgive them
that trespass against us,

10:08.651 --> 10:10.914
for ever and ever.
Amen.

10:10.958 --> 10:12.437
- Amen.

10:13.047 --> 10:15.223
[church bell ringing]

10:15.876 --> 10:20.750
- I'm not sure yet,
but I think so.

10:23.057 --> 10:25.146
I like her and...

10:25.189 --> 10:25.233
Honestly she's the best thing

10:26.364 --> 10:28.889
that could have happened
to me right now.

10:29.933 --> 10:32.457
- Nothing happens by chance.

10:33.807 --> 10:38.246
Do you know what word never
appears in the Bible?

10:38.289 --> 10:39.334
- No...

10:40.596 --> 10:41.858
No, no one's hired me
to correct that yet.

10:41.902 --> 10:42.380
[Father Andrew chuckles]

10:44.252 --> 10:44.339
Fate.

10:47.211 --> 10:49.561
The concept of fate is

10:49.605 --> 10:49.997
not part of
the Christian religion,

10:53.870 --> 10:54.088
and destiny...

10:55.742 --> 10:57.787
doesn't exist,

10:57.831 --> 10:57.961
except in our vocation
to give and receive love.

11:04.228 --> 11:04.359
Something you deserve
more than anything.

11:09.538 --> 11:12.106
- I'm really happy with her.

11:13.324 --> 11:16.327
We've got so much in common.

11:16.676 --> 11:18.895
She's funny...

11:19.766 --> 11:23.247
And she's always smiling...

11:23.291 --> 11:23.595
She even likes
classical music!

11:25.728 --> 11:27.512
- What's her name?

11:27.556 --> 11:27.817
- Catherine.
- Ah...

11:29.993 --> 11:34.215
From the Greek,
Katharos.

11:35.564 --> 11:38.306
Just let yourself go.

11:38.436 --> 11:41.352
Don't overthink things.

11:41.396 --> 11:41.483
Open up your eyes,

11:43.398 --> 11:46.706
and open yourself up
to life!

11:47.184 --> 11:49.404
Your mother would be
so pleased.

11:49.447 --> 11:52.233
- My mother would be
celebrating!

11:53.234 --> 11:58.108
- Have you started to sort
through her things to--

11:58.152 --> 11:59.631
- No, not yet.

11:59.675 --> 11:59.849
But I will...

12:01.285 --> 12:01.590
I will.

12:02.678 --> 12:02.852
- Well...

12:04.811 --> 12:08.553
If you need me,
you know what to do.

12:10.555 --> 12:12.383
- Thank you.

12:13.820 --> 12:14.951
[sighs]

12:14.995 --> 12:16.083
- The most absurd
part of it all

12:16.126 --> 12:18.912
was his reaction
after I played it.

12:18.955 --> 12:19.434
- What did he say?

12:21.131 --> 12:21.218
- "Capriccio No. 24,
Miss Gray...

12:23.743 --> 12:26.615
"How dare you think you could
tackle the absolute master,

12:26.658 --> 12:27.921
"the virtuoso!

12:27.964 --> 12:29.139
"Shame on you!

12:29.183 --> 12:30.924
You barely know how
to hold the violin!"

12:30.967 --> 12:32.926
[Catherine chuckles]

12:32.969 --> 12:33.143
After that you'd think
he would have left,

12:35.276 --> 12:36.320
but no.

12:36.364 --> 12:39.846
He just stood there,
staring at me!

12:41.499 --> 12:43.937
- And like Paganini himself,
you shouted back:

12:43.980 --> 12:45.808
"Catherine Gray
does not fail!"

12:45.852 --> 12:48.332
- [laughing]

12:49.986 --> 12:52.075
Did you know...

12:52.206 --> 12:55.296
Paganini was stick thin,

12:55.339 --> 12:56.036
toothless,

12:57.254 --> 12:59.648
and his fingertips
were covered in scars

12:59.691 --> 13:01.258
from all those years
of practice.

13:01.302 --> 13:04.087
- He wasn't much to look at,

13:04.131 --> 13:04.392
but he was really popular,

13:06.220 --> 13:08.788
especially with the ladies.

13:08.831 --> 13:09.179
He was a true star.

13:12.269 --> 13:14.358
- That's what they say...

13:15.055 --> 13:17.144
All I know is that I wouldn't go
to those extremes

13:17.187 --> 13:19.363
just to be like him.

13:19.407 --> 13:19.537
I like my hands too much!

13:25.195 --> 13:27.807
[dramatic music swells]

13:27.850 --> 13:29.809
♪♪

13:35.031 --> 13:37.164
[Catherine chuckles]

13:39.601 --> 13:41.646
♪♪

14:16.986 --> 14:19.249
[wind blowing]

14:23.253 --> 14:25.081
[Catherine gasps]

14:25.125 --> 14:27.170
[panting]

14:27.997 --> 14:30.086
[eerie violin music]

14:30.130 --> 14:32.262
♪♪

14:42.055 --> 14:44.753
[indistinct whispers]

15:06.514 --> 15:09.256
[metronome clicking]

15:16.437 --> 15:18.265
[violin music]

15:18.308 --> 15:20.310
♪♪

15:20.571 --> 15:23.139
- Cherry or apricot?

15:27.970 --> 15:30.407
Cherry or apricot?

15:39.895 --> 15:40.940
Cherry or apricot?

15:40.983 --> 15:42.811
- Sorry.
[chuckles]

15:42.942 --> 15:44.204
- Don't worry.

15:44.247 --> 15:44.334
Which do you prefer?

15:45.988 --> 15:47.685
- I can't decide.

15:47.729 --> 15:48.077
Both!

15:49.078 --> 15:50.950
- Excellent choice!

15:51.472 --> 15:53.213
You know they're homemade!

15:54.431 --> 15:56.129
What time's your class?

15:56.259 --> 15:57.347
- Three.

15:57.478 --> 15:58.609
- Do you want me
to come with you?

15:58.653 --> 16:00.002
- No.

16:00.524 --> 16:01.264
- Are you sure?

16:01.308 --> 16:01.438
- Yes!

16:02.352 --> 16:04.789
I can take care of myself.

16:06.400 --> 16:08.358
[violin playing resumes]

16:08.402 --> 16:10.056
♪♪

16:18.716 --> 16:20.588
[gasps]

16:22.111 --> 16:24.940
[eerie violin screeching]

16:42.697 --> 16:45.047
[gasping]
No!

16:58.539 --> 17:00.367
- Hey.
Are you okay?

17:00.541 --> 17:03.326
- It's alright.
It's alright.

17:08.069 --> 17:09.854
[whispers]
Hey...

17:12.335 --> 17:14.642
[door lock clicking]

17:16.905 --> 17:19.690
[door closes]
Hey, how are you?

17:20.778 --> 17:24.694
Yeah, I just got in.
There was a bit of traffic.

17:26.654 --> 17:29.439
Hey, don't worry about it,
okay?

17:29.483 --> 17:34.096
The doctor said so himself,
it was just stress.

17:34.575 --> 17:37.708
Okay.
You get some rest.

17:40.668 --> 17:43.714
I'll speak to you later.
Bye.

17:57.250 --> 17:59.382
[ominous music swells]

17:59.426 --> 18:01.428
♪♪

18:02.037 --> 18:04.126
[rosary clinking]

18:06.911 --> 18:09.000
[ominous music]

18:09.044 --> 18:11.002
♪♪

18:33.155 --> 18:34.809
- It's okay.
C'mon.

18:36.593 --> 18:37.681
- Okay.
- Okay.

18:37.725 --> 18:39.118
- Don't let me walk into--
- No. No.

18:39.161 --> 18:40.597
Stop. Stop.

18:44.123 --> 18:47.256
- Ta-dah!
- Surprise!

18:47.387 --> 18:50.607
[both singing]
Happy birthday to you...

18:50.651 --> 18:51.391
Happy birthday to you...

18:53.393 --> 18:56.570
Happy birthday,
dear Philip...

18:56.613 --> 18:57.048
Happy birthday to you!

19:01.314 --> 19:03.794
- Happy birthday!

19:04.491 --> 19:06.057
[both chuckles]

19:08.451 --> 19:09.409
- Oh! Wait, wait!

19:09.452 --> 19:11.280
Photo time!

19:12.325 --> 19:13.152
Okay.

19:13.195 --> 19:15.850
Get closer, get closer!

19:15.893 --> 19:16.024
No battery!

19:17.634 --> 19:17.808
- Get mine,
it's on my desk.

19:19.158 --> 19:19.375
- Okay!

19:19.941 --> 19:21.334
Be right back!

19:21.377 --> 19:23.249
Don't cut it without me!

19:29.516 --> 19:31.431
- Who made the cake?

19:32.780 --> 19:35.565
- He wants to know
who made the cake!

19:35.609 --> 19:36.262
- I did!
He just doesn't believe me!

19:44.487 --> 19:46.446
[distant child laughing]

19:50.711 --> 19:52.408
[eerie violin music]

19:52.452 --> 19:54.454
♪♪

20:03.680 --> 20:05.726
[child laughter continues]

20:05.769 --> 20:07.206
[door creaks open]

20:07.771 --> 20:10.339
- I had a word
with Father Earnest.

20:10.383 --> 20:10.470
Everything's going to charity.

20:12.167 --> 20:14.213
- Everything!
That's great!
- Uh-huh.

20:14.256 --> 20:14.561
- You know,

20:16.519 --> 20:16.693
Catherine could
give it a go.

20:19.957 --> 20:20.784
- Here I am!

20:20.828 --> 20:23.004
Did someone say my name?

20:24.701 --> 20:28.357
- We were just complimenting you
on your culinary expertise.

20:28.401 --> 20:29.706
[Catherine laughing]

20:29.750 --> 20:29.880
- Very funny, Father!

20:32.013 --> 20:34.407
- Are we taking this photo?

20:34.624 --> 20:35.930
- First...

20:35.973 --> 20:38.019
a surprise!

20:39.107 --> 20:40.282
Ta-dah!

20:40.326 --> 20:41.849
[Catherine chuckles]

20:43.503 --> 20:45.287
- Where did you find that?

20:45.331 --> 20:46.375
- It's a secret.

20:46.419 --> 20:49.552
It's a secret between
me and him!

20:52.990 --> 20:54.427
What?!

20:55.732 --> 20:57.995
- These things happen!

20:58.126 --> 21:00.433
- What things?

21:00.476 --> 21:00.607
- You know...

21:02.173 --> 21:05.655
People find things that
they thought they'd lost

21:05.699 --> 21:07.701
years ago.

21:09.224 --> 21:11.792
- Okay, um...

21:12.793 --> 21:15.230
Did she tell you
where she found it?

21:15.274 --> 21:18.277
- In the storage closet.

21:18.755 --> 21:22.411
Look, I want to believe
that this is a fluke.

21:22.759 --> 21:24.805
[Father Andrew exhales]
[chuckles]

21:27.329 --> 21:29.288
Philip,

21:30.550 --> 21:31.812
can we...

21:31.855 --> 21:35.990
can we just examine
the signs?

21:37.687 --> 21:39.689
The rosary...

21:40.211 --> 21:42.213
unwinds itself

21:42.257 --> 21:42.649
and you find it
on the floor.

21:44.781 --> 21:44.912
Next,
your sister's teddy bear--

21:47.784 --> 21:48.481
long-lost,
forgotten--

21:50.352 --> 21:57.751
mysteriously and inexplicably
reappears.

22:00.406 --> 22:04.671
The most cunning trick
of the devil

22:04.714 --> 22:05.280
is to try and convince one
he doesn't exist.

22:11.242 --> 22:16.857
But the one thing the devil
has never learned to do,

22:16.900 --> 22:18.032
and that is to
hide his tail!

22:23.080 --> 22:24.952
Ominously,

22:25.213 --> 22:29.522
I think you and I
have seen his tail.

22:29.565 --> 22:35.745
- I'm telling you,
nothing strange is going on!

22:37.921 --> 22:39.227
I'm sorry,

22:39.270 --> 22:43.710
but I won't allow the past
to ruin the present.

22:44.275 --> 22:47.366
- At least pray.

22:48.454 --> 22:50.934
The power of prayer

22:50.978 --> 22:51.326
is the strongest weapon
we have against all evil.

23:01.554 --> 23:03.817
[waves crashing]
[seagulls squawking]

23:06.385 --> 23:08.604
[eerie music swells]

23:08.648 --> 23:10.301
♪♪

23:13.217 --> 23:15.481
- Is everything okay?

23:15.959 --> 23:17.570
- Sure.

23:18.658 --> 23:20.355
- Sure?

23:21.138 --> 23:24.315
You know I can tell
when your mind drifts off.

23:30.060 --> 23:31.975
Philip, I'm serious.

23:32.019 --> 23:32.236
What's wrong?

23:34.674 --> 23:36.502
- It's nothing.

23:38.112 --> 23:40.288
- You're thinking about Piggy,
aren't you?

23:41.071 --> 23:43.857
I told you,
I just found him!

23:45.511 --> 23:47.034
- It's just that...

23:47.077 --> 23:50.429
My mother and I looked
everywhere for that,

23:50.472 --> 23:51.081
for years,

23:51.821 --> 23:54.607
and never found it.

23:56.086 --> 23:57.479
It was my sister's.

23:57.523 --> 23:59.263
- So...

23:59.307 --> 23:59.350
Aren't you happy
we found him now?

24:02.223 --> 24:04.355
- Yeah, of course.

24:04.791 --> 24:06.270
Of course.

24:08.316 --> 24:11.058
So I did have one idea...

24:11.101 --> 24:11.624
- Okay.

24:14.540 --> 24:17.194
- I'll be--
Wait, wait, wait!

24:17.238 --> 24:17.456
I'll be the director,

24:18.935 --> 24:21.024
and you be the star!

24:21.285 --> 24:23.374
Are you ready?
- No.

24:23.505 --> 24:25.507
- "Catherine at the Beach."

24:25.551 --> 24:26.639
Take one.

24:26.682 --> 24:26.943
Three, two, one,

24:28.205 --> 24:29.685
Action!

24:30.599 --> 24:32.340
- Is this okay?

24:32.383 --> 24:32.558
- You gotta keep going!

24:36.475 --> 24:38.651
[laughing]
- My head's spinning!

24:40.566 --> 24:42.742
My head's spinning!

25:04.894 --> 25:06.983
[eerie music]

25:07.027 --> 25:09.072
♪♪

25:36.622 --> 25:38.754
[distant footsteps]

25:39.886 --> 25:41.061
- Catherine?

25:56.946 --> 25:58.469
[distant thud]

25:59.122 --> 26:00.471
Catherine?

26:33.287 --> 26:35.681
[fast paced footsteps]

26:37.334 --> 26:39.119
Catherine?

26:46.126 --> 26:48.694
[footsteps continue]

27:02.011 --> 27:04.666
[distant heavy breathing]

27:19.725 --> 27:21.204
Catherine!

27:23.293 --> 27:26.383
[Catherine breathing heavily]

27:31.214 --> 27:33.173
[eerie violin music builds]

27:33.216 --> 27:35.610
♪♪

27:35.741 --> 27:37.743
[screaming]

27:52.888 --> 27:53.672
- Where is she?

27:53.715 --> 27:55.412
- She's in Isidore's room.

27:59.112 --> 28:01.505
[ominous music]

28:01.549 --> 28:03.725
♪♪

28:10.340 --> 28:12.299
- Don't come in.

28:20.524 --> 28:21.917
Catherine?

28:23.658 --> 28:26.443
[ominous music swells]
♪♪

28:34.625 --> 28:36.715
In the name of God,

28:37.106 --> 28:38.760
look at me.

28:39.456 --> 28:40.719
Philip!

28:40.762 --> 28:40.980
Go away!

28:48.509 --> 28:50.467
- Don't hurt her!

28:50.511 --> 28:50.598
- Help me!

28:51.817 --> 28:53.644
- If you want to save her,

28:53.688 --> 28:55.646
do not be deceived!

28:55.690 --> 28:57.997
- Hold her down!

28:58.214 --> 29:00.913
- Help me...

29:00.956 --> 29:01.130
[intense music]

29:03.176 --> 29:04.873
♪♪

29:19.627 --> 29:22.282
- Et Spiritus Sancti...

29:25.981 --> 29:29.071
In nómine Patris,

29:29.115 --> 29:33.641
et Fílii,
et Spíritus Sancti.

29:39.821 --> 29:43.259
In the name of Jesus Christ,

29:43.303 --> 29:43.782
our Lord and Savior,

29:46.959 --> 29:50.136
strengthened
by the intercession

29:50.179 --> 29:53.008
of the immaculate Virgin Mary,

29:53.052 --> 29:53.574
Mother of God,

29:55.750 --> 29:56.229
of blessed Michael
the Archangel,

30:00.407 --> 30:01.277
of the blessed Apostles
Peter and Paul

30:04.237 --> 30:05.760
and all the Saints,

30:05.804 --> 30:11.548
we confidently undertake
to repulse the attacks

30:11.592 --> 30:15.248
and deceits of the devil.

30:15.814 --> 30:18.338
Let the Lord God arise,

30:18.381 --> 30:18.817
and let His enemies
be scattered

30:21.254 --> 30:21.645
and let those that hate Him
flee from before His face.

30:27.129 --> 30:28.565
As the smoke vanishes,

30:29.740 --> 30:30.089
so let them vanish away:

30:32.656 --> 30:33.092
as the wax melts
before the fire,

30:36.138 --> 30:36.747
so let the wicked perish

30:40.316 --> 30:43.842
at the presence
of the Lord.

30:44.320 --> 30:49.760
Behold the cross
of the Lord!

30:50.979 --> 30:54.635
I cast you out,
unclean spirit,

30:54.678 --> 30:55.418
along with every
satanic power

30:58.857 --> 30:59.596
of the enemy!

31:04.297 --> 31:07.256
[demonic voice]
- I'm not going anywhere,
fucking priest!

31:07.300 --> 31:08.910
[demonic laughter]

31:09.128 --> 31:10.477
[door slams shut]

31:11.565 --> 31:15.264
- Unclean spirit be gone!

31:15.395 --> 31:17.092
Whoever you are,

31:17.136 --> 31:20.269
along with all your companions

31:20.313 --> 31:21.967
[Catherine choking]

31:22.010 --> 31:25.666
who possess this
servant of God!

31:25.709 --> 31:26.449
[Catherine screaming]

31:30.671 --> 31:35.110
[demonic voice]
- This girl is mine!
You know that, Philip?

31:38.853 --> 31:42.117
[demonic voice]
Did you go to confession
after you fucked her?

31:42.161 --> 31:42.857
- By the mysteries
of the Incarnation,

31:46.774 --> 31:49.342
the Sufferings and Death,

31:49.385 --> 31:49.908
the Resurrection,
and the Ascension

31:51.822 --> 31:54.129
of Our Lord Jesus Christ...

31:54.173 --> 31:57.567
by the sending
of the Holy Spirit;

31:57.611 --> 32:00.092
and the Coming of Our Lord

32:00.135 --> 32:02.485
unto the Last Judgment,

32:02.529 --> 32:04.487
I command you:

32:04.531 --> 32:09.971
Tell me, with some sign,
your name,

32:10.015 --> 32:10.798
the day,

32:11.277 --> 32:15.150
the time
of your damnation!

32:15.194 --> 32:15.498
[demonic voice]
- I am everything!

32:18.197 --> 32:20.634
[demonic voice]
I am chaos,

32:20.677 --> 32:20.939
[demonic voice]
temptation, destruction,

32:22.723 --> 32:24.464
[demonic voice]
damnation!

32:24.507 --> 32:27.989
[demonic voice]
I am the poison of your
miserable existences!

32:28.033 --> 32:28.511
[demonic voice]
I...

32:29.817 --> 32:30.470
[demonic voice]
Am...

32:31.471 --> 32:32.863
[demonic voice]
The Almighty!

32:33.299 --> 32:35.344
[demonic laughter]

32:36.128 --> 32:38.869
- Unclean spirit,

32:38.913 --> 32:39.566
retire!

32:40.436 --> 32:42.873
Satan be gone!

32:44.092 --> 32:46.921
Leave this woman!

32:47.182 --> 32:48.879
In the name of the Father,

32:48.923 --> 32:49.184
and of the Son,

32:50.142 --> 32:52.666
and of the Holy Spirit!

32:54.015 --> 32:58.367
The Word made Flesh
commands you.

32:58.411 --> 32:58.977
Jesus of Nazareth
commands you--

33:01.327 --> 33:02.981
[thud]

33:04.199 --> 33:06.549
[Philip panting]

33:15.080 --> 33:17.256
[demonic voice]
- Come on.

33:17.299 --> 33:17.386
[demonic voice]
Pray, Philip!

33:21.782 --> 33:26.178
[demonic voice]
Say all those little
prayers you know,

33:26.308 --> 33:28.702
[demonic voice]
every last one!

33:32.097 --> 33:38.712
[demonic voice]
Especially the ones that
whore of a mother taught you!

33:39.060 --> 33:42.237
[demonic voice]
Everyone knew her
in Church!

33:42.368 --> 33:46.459
[demonic voice]
Men knew her really well.

33:46.589 --> 33:50.071
[demonic voice]
While you were reading
your precious prayer cards,

33:50.115 --> 33:55.685
[demonic voice]
your mummy was busy getting
fucked in the sacristy!

33:57.035 --> 33:59.385
[clock ticking]

34:01.126 --> 34:03.302
[clock stops]

34:08.263 --> 34:10.135
[light piano music]

34:10.178 --> 34:12.005
♪♪

34:14.487 --> 34:16.663
[door bell ringing]

34:52.916 --> 34:54.962
[bell ringing]

35:10.064 --> 35:12.022
[eerie music swells]

35:12.066 --> 35:13.459
♪♪

35:46.492 --> 35:49.408
[windows rattling]
[bells ringing]

36:01.376 --> 36:04.292
[whispering prayers]

36:09.645 --> 36:12.735
[windows rattling]
[bells ringing]

36:36.498 --> 36:38.631
[doorbell ringing]

36:42.983 --> 36:45.203
[birds chirping]

37:00.174 --> 37:02.220
[cellphone ringing]

37:11.838 --> 37:13.100
- Hello?

37:13.143 --> 37:13.187
[violin playing over phone]

37:17.147 --> 37:19.237
Hello?

37:19.498 --> 37:21.587
[violin continues]

37:23.893 --> 37:25.939
Hello?
Who is this?

37:31.684 --> 37:34.556
[man speaking on TV]

37:48.483 --> 37:50.398
[knocking on door]

37:54.794 --> 37:57.753
[knocking continues]

38:29.655 --> 38:30.786
Hello?

38:31.178 --> 38:33.136
- Am I disturbing you?

38:34.442 --> 38:35.835
- No.

38:35.965 --> 38:38.490
- Are you okay?
Yes?

38:38.794 --> 38:40.318
- Uh... Yeah.
Yeah.

38:40.361 --> 38:41.928
Did you need something?

38:41.971 --> 38:42.929
- Yes.

38:42.972 --> 38:45.323
Do you have any salt?

38:45.366 --> 38:45.584
- Sure.
Hold on a minute.

38:49.544 --> 38:50.458
Here.

38:52.417 --> 38:54.288
- Thanks.

38:54.984 --> 38:59.685
Goodnight,
and enjoy your dinner.

39:00.816 --> 39:02.296
- Goodnight.

39:02.731 --> 39:04.342
- Bye.

39:05.778 --> 39:07.127
[door slams shut]

39:42.858 --> 39:45.208
[door creaking open]

39:49.648 --> 39:51.737
[eerie music swells]

39:51.780 --> 39:53.869
♪♪

40:29.731 --> 40:31.211
[door slams shut]

40:33.431 --> 40:35.998
[bells jingling]

41:07.769 --> 41:10.816
- I don't know how
this could have happened.

41:12.339 --> 41:16.430
- It looks as though
someone's having a joke!

41:16.474 --> 41:17.300
- Father!

41:18.563 --> 41:21.391
- No, no, no.
Please, don't get me wrong.

41:21.435 --> 41:23.655
It's just--

41:24.351 --> 41:27.485
Look,
has anybody else been here?

41:27.528 --> 41:28.834
- No!

41:31.576 --> 41:32.925
Yes.

41:33.403 --> 41:34.187
- What?!

41:34.230 --> 41:35.841
- Well she didn't come in.

41:35.884 --> 41:38.104
She lives upstairs.

41:38.147 --> 41:38.234
- What did she want?

41:39.627 --> 41:42.412
- She needed salt.

41:48.593 --> 41:51.030
- First things first.

41:54.729 --> 41:56.818
Let's just...

41:57.689 --> 42:01.954
put this back
where it belongs.

42:12.268 --> 42:13.792
Let's pray.

42:15.358 --> 42:16.969
[together]
- Our Father,

42:17.012 --> 42:19.014
who art in heaven...

42:22.017 --> 42:24.280
[cellphone ringing]

42:29.372 --> 42:30.591
- Hello?

42:30.722 --> 42:33.594
[violin playing over phone]

42:36.684 --> 42:38.033
Hello?

42:38.077 --> 42:39.774
[book crashes]

42:40.862 --> 42:43.386
[panting]

43:10.762 --> 43:12.677
[whispering]
Thy kingdom come,
thy will be done,

43:12.720 --> 43:14.156
on Earth
as it is in Heaven.

43:14.200 --> 43:15.941
Give us this day
our daily bread

43:15.984 --> 43:17.333
and forgive us
our trespasses

43:17.377 --> 43:19.640
as we forgive those
who trespass against us

43:19.684 --> 43:21.250
and lead us not
into temptation

43:21.294 --> 43:22.774
but deliver us from evil.

43:22.817 --> 43:25.211
Hail Mary, full of Grace,
the Lord is with thee.

43:25.254 --> 43:27.300
[thunder crack]

43:34.524 --> 43:36.439
[windows rattling]

43:45.666 --> 43:47.929
[bells jingling]

44:02.378 --> 44:05.033
bell jingling intensifies]

44:06.208 --> 44:08.820
[mumbles prayers]

44:16.044 --> 44:18.351
[toy winding up]

44:22.790 --> 44:24.836
[toy clattering]

45:04.832 --> 45:06.747
[thunder cracks]

45:09.097 --> 45:11.578
[match strikes]

45:14.450 --> 45:17.236
[eerie music swells]

45:17.279 --> 45:19.281
♪♪

45:34.862 --> 45:37.691
[mumbling to self]

46:22.910 --> 46:25.260
[electrical buzzing]

46:50.198 --> 46:52.635
[rosary jingling]

47:21.969 --> 47:23.971
[marbles spilling]

47:31.849 --> 47:33.589
- I'm sorry!

47:33.720 --> 47:35.156
I knocked, but...

47:35.200 --> 47:37.767
but the door
was already open.

47:37.898 --> 47:39.944
I think it's broken.

47:39.987 --> 47:40.031
- That's not possible.

47:41.641 --> 47:44.122
- Try if you want...

47:45.297 --> 47:47.038
[door creaks closed]

47:51.869 --> 47:55.263
See?
It opens.

47:56.221 --> 47:57.657
Don't worry.

47:57.700 --> 48:00.834
It's probably just some stupid
problem with the lock.

48:00.878 --> 48:02.488
Nothing major.

48:02.531 --> 48:05.012
A locksmith can fix it.

48:10.452 --> 48:12.150
Are you okay?

48:12.193 --> 48:14.456
- Yeah... Yeah...

48:14.500 --> 48:14.717
- Okay,

48:15.457 --> 48:16.894
sit down.

48:21.855 --> 48:23.770
[eerie violin music]

48:23.813 --> 48:25.772
♪♪

48:28.514 --> 48:31.169
Stay like that for about
twenty minutes

48:31.212 --> 48:31.734
and then put
some cream on it.

48:33.693 --> 48:33.780
Do you have any?

48:34.912 --> 48:37.871
- Yeah, I think
I've got some somewhere.

48:42.571 --> 48:43.964
- I should go.

48:51.885 --> 48:55.019
If you need anything at all,
just give me a shout.

48:56.237 --> 48:58.936
Or pray,
if you prefer.

49:01.764 --> 49:04.071
[door opens/closes]

49:07.074 --> 49:08.249
- Her name is Sonia.

49:08.293 --> 49:11.383
I've seen her
a couple of times now.

49:12.079 --> 49:13.994
- Oh, really?

49:14.125 --> 49:15.909
[crunching on cookie]

49:15.953 --> 49:17.041
- Mm-hmm.

49:17.084 --> 49:18.085
She made these.

49:18.129 --> 49:20.870
They're her specialty.
Try one.

49:22.742 --> 49:24.352
- Philip...

49:25.092 --> 49:28.704
You... you rang me,
distraught.

49:28.748 --> 49:32.926
All the bells were ringing,
you said.

49:32.970 --> 49:33.231
Was this perhaps not the wind
blowing them?

49:38.758 --> 49:40.499
- Maybe.

49:41.717 --> 49:45.504
No. All the windows and doors
were closed.

49:45.547 --> 49:45.939
- Okay...

49:47.419 --> 49:47.767
And what about the...

49:50.291 --> 49:53.251
the creature that
was following you?

49:53.294 --> 49:57.037
Nothing?
Your imagination?

49:58.082 --> 50:02.173
- Look, is this key
my imagination?

50:07.352 --> 50:12.879
- You really don't know
what this key opens?

50:12.922 --> 50:13.053
- I've no idea!

50:14.881 --> 50:16.100
- You know, she didn't have
to make these.

50:16.143 --> 50:17.971
She's actually
quite a nice person.

50:18.015 --> 50:20.017
- Yes,

50:20.321 --> 50:22.889
I'm sure she is.

50:24.369 --> 50:28.242
Would you like me
to look after this?

50:29.026 --> 50:31.724
- No, I'll hold on to it.

50:34.770 --> 50:36.033
- Okay.

50:40.994 --> 50:43.083
- Wait, what now?

50:45.694 --> 50:48.262
- I really don't know.

50:48.697 --> 50:51.048
But since you ask...

50:51.091 --> 50:51.135
For both your sakes,
I think you

50:53.833 --> 50:54.225
shouldn't see Sonia again.

51:04.148 --> 51:07.064
[door closes]
[crunching on cookies]

51:08.108 --> 51:09.370
- "He approached her

51:09.414 --> 51:12.547
"as he inhaled the smell
of her jet black hair.

51:12.591 --> 51:14.245
"She was beautiful,

51:14.288 --> 51:19.859
with thin lips
and perfect almond eyes."

51:22.862 --> 51:25.560
[footsteps approaching]

51:34.352 --> 51:36.136
Hi, Sonia!

51:36.267 --> 51:37.877
- Hi, Philip!

51:37.920 --> 51:38.617
How are you?

51:38.660 --> 51:40.401
- I'm okay.

51:40.445 --> 51:41.402
- How's your back?

51:41.446 --> 51:43.230
- Better, thanks!

51:43.274 --> 51:44.405
- Did you put some
cream on it?

51:44.449 --> 51:45.928
- Yeah, I did!

51:45.972 --> 51:47.147
- Okay.

51:47.191 --> 51:49.236
- I was just checking out
the new lock.

51:49.280 --> 51:49.671
- So, problem solved?

51:51.760 --> 51:53.110
- Yeah.

51:53.153 --> 51:53.545
Um, I don't--

51:55.634 --> 51:56.200
I was just about
to have dinner.

51:57.505 --> 51:59.942
I don't know if you
fancied joining me?

51:59.986 --> 52:00.160
- Yeah. Sure.
Why not?

52:02.336 --> 52:02.858
- Yeah?

52:03.903 --> 52:05.078
- Okay.
But I'm cooking!

52:05.122 --> 52:05.513
- Okay.

52:06.688 --> 52:07.776
- See you later!

52:07.820 --> 52:09.909
- See you in a minute!

52:19.440 --> 52:22.008
[cellphone vibrating]

52:23.009 --> 52:24.837
[dishes clattering]

52:33.324 --> 52:36.631
- Spaghetti with tomatoes.

52:37.415 --> 52:38.590
- It looks amazing!

52:38.633 --> 52:40.069
- I hope you like it.

52:40.113 --> 52:42.028
And a little wine...

52:42.159 --> 52:44.770
Oh... Please.

52:46.511 --> 52:49.035
It's my favorite.

52:53.387 --> 52:54.214
Let's toast.

52:54.258 --> 52:56.216
- Cheers!
- No.

52:56.347 --> 52:59.611
You've got to look me
into my eyes,

52:59.872 --> 53:02.875
or it's no sex
for seven years.

53:03.484 --> 53:04.790
Cheers!

53:04.920 --> 53:06.095
- Cheers.

53:16.105 --> 53:17.716
- Oh my God,
this is amazing!

53:17.759 --> 53:20.066
- Do you like it?

53:20.240 --> 53:21.328
- It's really good!

53:21.372 --> 53:23.200
Did you invent this?

53:23.374 --> 53:24.636
- More or less.

53:24.679 --> 53:26.028
- What does that mean?

53:26.072 --> 53:26.290
- It's more of a personal
reinterpretation.

53:31.556 --> 53:31.817
Have some more wine.

53:34.036 --> 53:35.864
[wine pouring]

53:39.694 --> 53:41.000
Cheers!

53:41.740 --> 53:43.350
[glasses clink]

53:46.658 --> 53:47.615
[pounds on table]

53:47.659 --> 53:49.400
Music!

53:51.837 --> 53:54.056
What do you listen to?

53:54.361 --> 53:56.276
Chopin?

53:56.581 --> 53:59.105
This is so old!

53:59.148 --> 53:59.410
Ooh.

54:01.716 --> 54:03.588
I like it!

54:13.424 --> 54:15.426
[jazz music plays]
♪♪

54:15.948 --> 54:17.515
Dance with me.

54:17.558 --> 54:17.732
- Oh no,
I can't dance.

54:19.125 --> 54:20.735
I really can't dance.

54:20.779 --> 54:21.954
- Please...

54:21.997 --> 54:23.260
dance with me.

54:23.303 --> 54:24.478
- No. You wouldn't
want me to dance,

54:24.522 --> 54:25.784
[nervous chuckle]
I'm not very good at it.

54:25.827 --> 54:27.742
- Dance with me.

54:39.754 --> 54:41.365
And you...

54:41.408 --> 54:41.626
What do you do?

54:42.844 --> 54:45.804
- Uh...
I'm a proofreader.

54:46.152 --> 54:47.545
- Cool!

54:47.588 --> 54:47.762
You must read a lot then.

54:50.678 --> 54:51.679
- Yeah.

54:51.723 --> 54:54.334
I just read and correct.

54:54.378 --> 54:54.639
- Me, too.

54:55.814 --> 54:55.988
I usually read
in my spare time.

54:58.991 --> 55:02.516
I like the classics.

55:02.560 --> 55:03.125
I like

55:04.779 --> 55:05.258
Italian writers.

55:07.478 --> 55:09.915
Maybe you know them.

55:10.394 --> 55:13.310
Such as Pirandello,

55:13.353 --> 55:13.875
Moravia,

55:14.920 --> 55:15.007
Svevo.

55:16.704 --> 55:17.009
Do you know them?

55:17.749 --> 55:19.011
- Yes.

55:19.794 --> 55:21.883
- Have some more wine.

55:23.668 --> 55:26.540
You need to loosen up.

55:30.544 --> 55:32.981
[eerie music swells]
♪♪

55:35.723 --> 55:38.247
Do you have anything sweet?

55:38.726 --> 55:40.032
- I think I might have
something.

55:40.075 --> 55:41.947
Nothing homemade though.

55:49.998 --> 55:51.435
- What do you have?

55:51.565 --> 55:53.915
- Here we go.

55:54.351 --> 55:56.788
It's a strawberry cheesecake.

55:56.831 --> 55:58.398
- Wow.

55:58.877 --> 56:01.401
I swear,
it's my favorite.

56:01.445 --> 56:02.010
- Really?

56:02.141 --> 56:03.360
- Yeah!

56:03.403 --> 56:06.972
But with that,
we need some shots.

56:12.978 --> 56:14.588
[woman's voice]
- Yes...

56:17.286 --> 56:18.897
- Sonia?

56:23.597 --> 56:25.512
Sonia, if that's you...

56:25.556 --> 56:28.297
can you tell me, alright?

56:33.694 --> 56:35.435
- Yes.

56:35.479 --> 56:35.696
It's right there..

56:38.482 --> 56:40.005
You see it?

56:40.309 --> 56:43.356
It's everywhere.

56:43.922 --> 56:47.404
It's looking at me.

56:47.882 --> 56:52.713
It's coming towards me.

56:53.584 --> 56:55.324
You see?

56:55.760 --> 56:58.458
It's like the night.

56:58.589 --> 57:02.593
It smells like wet earth.

57:02.636 --> 57:03.420
[shivering]
I'm cold!

57:07.467 --> 57:10.035
It's coming back!

57:10.775 --> 57:12.341
- Who are you?

57:12.820 --> 57:16.302
- Shh! Listen.

57:16.694 --> 57:19.218
We are relics,

57:19.261 --> 57:19.523
like screams
in the silence.

57:25.877 --> 57:28.009
It's fear.

57:29.097 --> 57:32.013
It's fear, Philip!

57:32.057 --> 57:32.144
[intense music]

57:34.059 --> 57:36.540
♪♪

57:42.023 --> 57:44.461
[panting]

57:45.636 --> 57:47.289
[knocking on door]

57:51.990 --> 57:54.035
[eerie violin music]

57:54.079 --> 57:56.081
♪♪

58:17.581 --> 58:19.887
- No, no, no, no, no!

58:24.370 --> 58:27.025
[fire crackling]

58:47.567 --> 58:49.526
- Are you okay?

58:49.874 --> 58:50.788
Will you talk to me?!

58:50.831 --> 58:52.311
- Just leave me alone!

58:52.441 --> 58:54.792
Leave me alone,
you won't understand!

58:54.922 --> 58:56.576
- Philip!
Philip, stop!

58:56.620 --> 58:58.360
What are you talking about?!

58:58.404 --> 58:59.666
- What am I talking about?

58:59.710 --> 59:02.147
I'm talking about the demon
that has kept me

59:02.190 --> 59:05.150
prisoner in this place
for the last two years!

59:05.716 --> 59:09.807
About how it's been tormenting
me most of my life!

59:09.850 --> 59:09.981
There was an old woman
in my room just now!

59:12.897 --> 59:13.506
She just appeared
out of thin air!

59:14.942 --> 59:16.857
- An old woman just appeared
out of thin air now?!

59:16.901 --> 59:18.380
- Yes!

59:18.903 --> 59:20.252
- Philip!

59:20.382 --> 59:21.340
You're scaring me!

59:21.383 --> 59:24.473
- I'm scared!
I'm...

59:25.126 --> 59:26.475
- You have...

59:27.215 --> 59:29.478
to calm down now.

59:29.522 --> 59:29.653
Okay?

59:49.977 --> 59:53.111
- Do you believe
in the devil?

59:54.329 --> 59:55.983
- I don't know.

59:57.028 --> 59:59.291
I've never been
very religious.

59:59.334 --> 59:59.639
- I'm not talking about
religion,

01:00:01.685 --> 01:00:02.120
or even evil
in the abstract sense,

01:00:07.255 --> 01:00:10.302
but the devil
in the flesh.

01:00:10.345 --> 01:00:10.781
A real being

01:00:11.912 --> 01:00:14.349
that haunts you
every second,

01:00:14.393 --> 01:00:17.091
of every day of your life.

01:00:18.702 --> 01:00:22.314
It's been tormenting me
since I was a child.

01:00:22.967 --> 01:00:24.969
- You're scaring me.

01:00:25.099 --> 01:00:28.625
- I also used to be terrified.

01:00:32.629 --> 01:00:35.240
My mother's prayers
were the only thing

01:00:35.283 --> 01:00:37.721
that could keep it away.

01:00:37.938 --> 01:00:42.813
It was as if her prayers
squashed it...

01:00:42.856 --> 01:00:43.291
Like they pushed him away.

01:00:50.647 --> 01:00:52.300
And then it...

01:00:52.431 --> 01:00:55.303
killed my sister Isidore.

01:00:57.610 --> 01:01:00.482
She had just turned seven.

01:01:05.879 --> 01:01:09.709
We got through that period
together.

01:01:09.927 --> 01:01:13.321
We gave each other strength.

01:01:16.063 --> 01:01:18.500
I never knew my father so...

01:01:18.544 --> 01:01:19.980
it was thanks to her

01:01:20.024 --> 01:01:22.896
that I even had
a normal childhood,

01:01:23.462 --> 01:01:25.812
like every other kid.

01:01:29.163 --> 01:01:30.730
We laughed,

01:01:32.253 --> 01:01:34.560
we played,

01:01:34.603 --> 01:01:34.778
and, most of all,
we prayed.

01:01:38.477 --> 01:01:41.741
Father Andrew told us that our
prayers would protect us

01:01:41.785 --> 01:01:44.570
more than anything else,

01:01:45.136 --> 01:01:46.790
and he was right.

01:01:48.139 --> 01:01:52.709
That... creature

01:01:53.797 --> 01:01:57.888
didn't return
for a very long time.

01:02:07.636 --> 01:02:08.942
Then,

01:02:09.116 --> 01:02:11.379
my mother passed away and

01:02:11.423 --> 01:02:11.597
I was left alone.

01:02:13.468 --> 01:02:13.599
[violin music playing]

01:02:15.819 --> 01:02:18.299
♪♪

01:02:25.176 --> 01:02:28.179
It was Catherine
that gave me the strength

01:02:28.222 --> 01:02:30.747
to get through that.

01:02:33.575 --> 01:02:36.491
We met by chance
a few months earlier.

01:02:38.537 --> 01:02:40.713
She was a violinist.

01:02:41.670 --> 01:02:43.977
I loved Chopin

01:02:44.325 --> 01:02:46.980
and she adored Paganini.

01:02:48.155 --> 01:02:52.377
I suppose we didn't see
eye to eye on music but...

01:02:52.899 --> 01:02:54.945
We fell in love.

01:02:58.513 --> 01:03:01.516
I really believed

01:03:01.690 --> 01:03:06.783
that I could have started
a new life with her.

01:03:10.003 --> 01:03:11.744
And then...

01:03:13.702 --> 01:03:17.532
And then that thing...

01:03:19.230 --> 01:03:22.407
Returned and took her away,

01:03:23.364 --> 01:03:25.584
possessed her.

01:03:25.714 --> 01:03:29.414
Her body and her soul.

01:03:32.809 --> 01:03:35.812
It just all happened
so suddenly,

01:03:37.204 --> 01:03:40.512
or maybe I was just
blinded by love...

01:03:41.730 --> 01:03:44.298
Father Andrew knew immediately

01:03:44.342 --> 01:03:46.823
that she had to be freed.

01:03:50.000 --> 01:03:53.220
But the exorcism failed.

01:03:53.655 --> 01:03:56.833
Since then I've
locked myself in here.

01:03:58.965 --> 01:04:01.707
She may not be here anymore,

01:04:05.363 --> 01:04:07.321
but I still believe
that my mother

01:04:07.365 --> 01:04:10.542
is watching over me
in this house.

01:04:12.152 --> 01:04:15.808
- Do you think this thing,

01:04:15.852 --> 01:04:16.113
this presence,

01:04:16.940 --> 01:04:18.376
is still after you?

01:04:18.419 --> 01:04:20.117
- Yes,

01:04:20.421 --> 01:04:22.815
he's always here.

01:04:23.163 --> 01:04:25.426
- If you don't feel safe,

01:04:26.645 --> 01:04:28.865
you could sleep
at my place.

01:04:29.474 --> 01:04:32.825
- Believe it or not,
I only feel safe here.

01:04:47.927 --> 01:04:49.886
[demonic voice]
- Come with me.

01:04:51.061 --> 01:04:53.802
[demonic voice]
Come with me.

01:05:18.001 --> 01:05:19.654
[demonic voice]
Come with me.

01:05:19.698 --> 01:05:19.916
[demonic voice]
Come with me.

01:05:50.468 --> 01:05:53.123
[wind howling]

01:06:05.570 --> 01:06:07.964
[panting]

01:06:08.007 --> 01:06:10.401
[wind howling]

01:06:13.795 --> 01:06:15.362
- Catherine?

01:06:17.364 --> 01:06:19.801
No!
No, wait!

01:07:24.779 --> 01:07:26.651
[dramatic music]

01:07:26.694 --> 01:07:28.609
♪♪

01:07:35.834 --> 01:07:40.665
- Death and Destruction
are never satisfied.

01:07:41.013 --> 01:07:42.710
- You're not real!

01:07:42.841 --> 01:07:46.540
[demonic voice]
- Death and Destruction
are never satisfied!

01:08:06.212 --> 01:08:08.475
[radio static buzzing]

01:08:11.913 --> 01:08:13.654
[Catherine's voice]
- No, wait!

01:08:13.698 --> 01:08:15.395
- Okay. How about now?

01:08:15.439 --> 01:08:17.528
- Okay... ready.

01:08:17.571 --> 01:08:18.006
- "Catherine at the Beach..."

01:08:20.399 --> 01:08:24.839
Three, two, one...
Action!

01:08:26.189 --> 01:08:27.407
[laughing]
- Is this okay?

01:08:27.451 --> 01:08:28.538
- Great!

01:08:29.888 --> 01:08:31.890
- My head's spinning!

01:08:32.804 --> 01:08:35.154
- Smile for the camera.

01:08:39.115 --> 01:08:41.247
Smile for the camera.

01:08:53.564 --> 01:08:55.957
[cellphone ringing]

01:08:58.002 --> 01:08:59.091
- Father?

01:08:59.135 --> 01:09:01.398
[violin music playing]

01:09:01.441 --> 01:09:03.139
Father?

01:09:04.792 --> 01:09:06.316
Hello?

01:09:10.624 --> 01:09:12.582
[eerie music]

01:09:12.626 --> 01:09:15.151
♪♪

01:09:33.734 --> 01:09:36.520
- Do you like my drawing?!

01:09:37.085 --> 01:09:39.218
Do you like my drawing?!

01:09:39.261 --> 01:09:39.697
[girl screaming]

01:09:57.280 --> 01:09:59.978
[Catherine gasps]

01:10:01.240 --> 01:10:02.720
- Catherine...

01:10:06.289 --> 01:10:08.987
- Save me.

01:10:20.607 --> 01:10:24.220
Save me.

01:10:30.661 --> 01:10:32.750
- No!

01:11:11.658 --> 01:11:13.225
Father?

01:11:15.096 --> 01:11:16.924
What are you doing here?

01:11:18.883 --> 01:11:20.624
- What's that...

01:11:20.667 --> 01:11:20.885
knife in your hand?

01:11:23.235 --> 01:11:23.322
- It's not what we thought.

01:11:26.978 --> 01:11:28.414
He's managed to get in.

01:11:28.458 --> 01:11:30.938
We have to stop him
once and for all!

01:11:30.982 --> 01:11:31.461
- Whose blood it that,
Philip?

01:11:34.507 --> 01:11:34.638
- What blood?

01:11:35.900 --> 01:11:35.943
- That blood on the knife,
Philip!

01:11:40.383 --> 01:11:42.428
- No. It's... It's not...

01:11:42.472 --> 01:11:46.040
It's from the cake
that me and Sonia had.

01:11:48.434 --> 01:11:50.871
- Where is Sonia?

01:11:51.611 --> 01:11:53.874
- I don't know!

01:11:53.918 --> 01:11:54.092
What does that have to do
with anything?!

01:11:55.267 --> 01:11:58.575
Did you hear me?
He's managed to get in!

01:11:59.271 --> 01:12:01.317
- Oh my God!

01:12:05.364 --> 01:12:09.281
There is no demon, Philip!

01:12:10.151 --> 01:12:12.284
- Are you crazy!

01:12:12.937 --> 01:12:15.635
What about everything
that's happened until now?

01:12:15.679 --> 01:12:16.288
- And what exactly has happened
up until now, Philip?!

01:12:19.683 --> 01:12:19.813
- The attacks!

01:12:21.337 --> 01:12:21.424
Catherine!

01:12:24.165 --> 01:12:26.777
- What does this key open,
Philip?

01:12:27.560 --> 01:12:29.388
- I don't know!

01:12:29.432 --> 01:12:29.519
- Where is Sonia?

01:12:31.564 --> 01:12:31.782
- I told you,
I don't know!!

01:12:35.176 --> 01:12:38.484
- When you last showed me
this key, Philip,

01:12:38.615 --> 01:12:41.008
I really began to think
that you understood

01:12:41.052 --> 01:12:43.097
exactly what you had done.

01:12:43.141 --> 01:12:44.360
I was wrong.

01:12:45.056 --> 01:12:48.233
You know exactly
what this key opens.

01:12:48.276 --> 01:12:48.755
You've given it to me
once before...

01:12:51.541 --> 01:12:55.066
Just after
you killed Catherine.

01:12:55.109 --> 01:12:55.283
You strangled her

01:12:57.068 --> 01:12:57.285
and hid her body
in the cupboard,

01:13:00.463 --> 01:13:00.550
then you gave me the key.

01:13:04.118 --> 01:13:09.559
May God forgive me
for having covered for you.

01:13:09.602 --> 01:13:10.473
- We both saw her
die that day!

01:13:12.344 --> 01:13:15.173
- That day never happened,
Philip!

01:13:15.739 --> 01:13:17.871
You have a sickness!

01:13:18.698 --> 01:13:20.744
Your mother
has been treating you

01:13:20.787 --> 01:13:23.573
ever since you were
a little boy.

01:13:24.008 --> 01:13:26.140
I was aware of it,

01:13:26.576 --> 01:13:30.754
and when she died and you
started having these...

01:13:30.797 --> 01:13:31.145
visions again,

01:13:32.973 --> 01:13:36.412
I made it my mission
to look after you.

01:13:37.151 --> 01:13:38.805
I failed.

01:13:43.549 --> 01:13:44.724
Now,

01:13:44.768 --> 01:13:44.985
see for yourself
where Sonia is.

01:13:56.867 --> 01:13:59.478
- Are you okay, Philip?

01:14:00.523 --> 01:14:02.307
- Just leave me alone.

01:14:20.630 --> 01:14:23.067
[Sonia screaming]

01:14:29.595 --> 01:14:32.032
- We'll find someone
who can give you

01:14:32.076 --> 01:14:34.600
the help you need.

01:14:35.862 --> 01:14:38.604
None of this is your fault,
Philip.

01:14:39.387 --> 01:14:44.131
It's the sickness
that drove you to it.

01:14:52.226 --> 01:14:55.360
[demonic voice]
- You are not crazy, Philip,

01:14:55.403 --> 01:14:55.665
[demonic voice]
but the priest is right.

01:14:57.754 --> 01:14:59.495
- Be quiet!

01:14:59.538 --> 01:15:03.237
[demonic voice]
- There is no demon
outside of yourself.

01:15:03.281 --> 01:15:03.890
[demonic voice]
Accept it!

01:15:05.457 --> 01:15:05.675
[demonic voice]
Ignore him!

01:15:07.328 --> 01:15:07.546
[demonic voice]
Kill him!

01:15:08.286 --> 01:15:10.244
- No, I can't do it.

01:15:10.288 --> 01:15:13.073
I can't do it.
Get out!

01:15:13.117 --> 01:15:13.596
- Calm down.

01:15:15.206 --> 01:15:16.686
We'll find a solution!

01:15:16.729 --> 01:15:17.121
[demonic voice]
- Liar!

01:15:18.644 --> 01:15:18.688
[demonic voice]
He'll have you
locked away again.

01:15:20.777 --> 01:15:21.299
[demonic voice]
This time forever!

01:15:22.996 --> 01:15:23.431
[demonic voice]
Kill him!

01:15:24.737 --> 01:15:26.652
- Be quiet!

01:15:27.348 --> 01:15:28.959
- Philip,

01:15:30.090 --> 01:15:32.266
calm down.

01:15:32.310 --> 01:15:32.658
Put the knife down.

01:15:34.617 --> 01:15:37.271
[demonic voice]
- Don't do it, Philip!

01:15:37.315 --> 01:15:37.358
[demonic voice]
Aren't you tired of all this?

01:15:41.275 --> 01:15:41.841
[demonic voice]
First, your mother,

01:15:44.365 --> 01:15:45.018
[demonic voice]
and now him!

01:15:47.020 --> 01:15:47.238
[demonic voice]
They repressed you,

01:15:49.153 --> 01:15:49.457
[demonic voice]
stuffed you with prayers
and drugs,

01:15:53.157 --> 01:15:56.073
[demonic voice]
and stupid superstition.

01:15:56.116 --> 01:15:56.552
[demonic voice]
You are so much
more than this!

01:15:59.946 --> 01:16:03.080
[demonic voice]
Free yourself!

01:16:04.908 --> 01:16:06.431
- I can't do it.

01:16:06.562 --> 01:16:07.606
I can't do it.

01:16:07.650 --> 01:16:09.608
I won't do it!

01:16:09.652 --> 01:16:09.782
Get out!
Get out!

01:16:12.176 --> 01:16:13.873
- Calm down!

01:16:13.917 --> 01:16:14.265
[demonic voice]
- I cannot go

01:16:15.962 --> 01:16:16.397
[demonic voice]
and you cannot
keep fearing me.

01:16:18.878 --> 01:16:19.400
[demonic voice]
Accept your true nature.

01:16:21.664 --> 01:16:22.055
[demonic voice]
Don't you want
to finally live?

01:16:24.318 --> 01:16:26.494
- Philip, listen to me!

01:16:26.538 --> 01:16:26.886
Pull yourself together!

01:16:28.671 --> 01:16:28.714
- You're right.

01:16:30.368 --> 01:16:32.675
You're right.

01:16:32.718 --> 01:16:32.849
[whispers]
There is no demon.

01:16:38.028 --> 01:16:39.899
[whispers]
There is no demon.

01:16:39.943 --> 01:16:40.073
[thud]
[grunt]

01:16:44.469 --> 01:16:46.689
[Father whimpering]

01:16:48.691 --> 01:16:50.475
[Philip screaming]

01:17:07.666 --> 01:17:09.625
I'm sorry, Father,

01:17:09.755 --> 01:17:12.889
but I deserve so much more.

01:17:13.280 --> 01:17:16.066
I deserve to be free.

01:17:16.109 --> 01:17:16.153
[Philip screaming]

01:17:23.726 --> 01:17:26.032
[bells jingling]

01:17:29.296 --> 01:17:31.124
[eerie violin music]

01:17:31.168 --> 01:17:33.039
♪♪

01:18:05.071 --> 01:18:08.205
[demonic voice]
- Now you truly are...

01:18:08.248 --> 01:18:11.643
[demonic voice]
what you are!

01:18:11.687 --> 01:18:11.991
[eerie music intensifies]

01:18:14.080 --> 01:18:16.604
♪♪

01:18:27.790 --> 01:18:29.792
[Catherine screaming]

01:18:39.323 --> 01:18:41.847
[Catherine gasping]

01:19:09.832 --> 01:19:12.051
- It's coming back!

01:19:14.140 --> 01:19:18.666
Death and Destruction
are never satisfied!

01:19:18.710 --> 01:19:18.928
[cellphone ringing]

01:19:29.721 --> 01:19:31.767
[clock ticking]

01:19:42.168 --> 01:19:43.822
- My grandmother
gave this to me

01:19:43.866 --> 01:19:45.215
when I was a little girl.

01:19:45.258 --> 01:19:46.607
Now,

01:19:46.651 --> 01:19:48.348
every time you're scared,

01:19:48.392 --> 01:19:50.611
hold it,
say a little prayer,

01:19:50.655 --> 01:19:53.005
and everything will go away.

01:19:53.049 --> 01:19:53.136
- The most cunning trick
of the devil

01:19:59.055 --> 01:20:04.756
is to try and convince you
that he doesn't exist.

01:20:05.322 --> 01:20:10.240
But the one thing the devil
has never learned to do

01:20:10.283 --> 01:20:10.762
is to hide his tail.

01:20:15.811 --> 01:20:18.770
Michael the Archangel...

01:20:18.814 --> 01:20:22.774
A true warrior!
Just like you.

01:20:22.905 --> 01:20:24.210
- One...

01:20:24.558 --> 01:20:26.212
Two...

01:20:26.256 --> 01:20:26.299
Three.

01:20:31.783 --> 01:20:34.351
[angelic voice harmonizing]

01:20:41.488 --> 01:20:43.969
- I tried to resist,

01:20:44.143 --> 01:20:47.755
but I can't go on
without your help.

01:20:48.278 --> 01:20:50.671
- Don't be afraid.

01:20:51.977 --> 01:20:53.805
- I'm evil!

01:20:53.936 --> 01:20:56.155
I've killed people!

01:20:56.199 --> 01:20:56.590
- He's deceived you.

01:20:58.331 --> 01:20:58.723
You are none
of those things.

01:21:01.030 --> 01:21:01.465
He knows this

01:21:02.640 --> 01:21:02.814
and it is why
he fears you.

01:21:06.731 --> 01:21:08.515
- Who am I?

01:21:09.125 --> 01:21:12.302
Please tell me,
I'm begging you!

01:21:12.432 --> 01:21:15.827
- Philip,
you know who you are.

01:21:15.871 --> 01:21:16.306
Trust yourself.

01:21:20.963 --> 01:21:24.662
I will always be with you.

01:21:25.750 --> 01:21:28.100
- I miss you.

01:21:30.363 --> 01:21:32.670
[dramatic music swells]

01:21:32.713 --> 01:21:34.715
♪♪

01:21:56.607 --> 01:21:59.349
[demonic voice]
- You're mine, Philip!

01:21:59.697 --> 01:22:01.307
[demonic voice]
Don't think you've won!

01:22:01.351 --> 01:22:04.441
[demonic voice]
You're far too weak,
you're nothing!

01:22:05.572 --> 01:22:07.792
- You didn't take me,

01:22:09.446 --> 01:22:12.231
and you won't take
her either!

01:22:16.932 --> 01:22:19.021
[dramatic orchestral music]

01:22:19.064 --> 01:22:21.023
♪♪

01:22:31.033 --> 01:22:33.252
[Catherine screaming]

01:22:35.211 --> 01:22:35.951
Our Father,

01:22:35.994 --> 01:22:36.908
- Let go!

01:22:36.952 --> 01:22:38.954
- who art in Heaven,

01:22:38.997 --> 01:22:41.434
hallowed be thy name.

01:22:41.652 --> 01:22:43.523
Thy kingdom come,

01:22:43.567 --> 01:22:43.697
thy will be done,

01:22:45.177 --> 01:22:47.310
on Earth
as it is in Heaven.

01:22:47.353 --> 01:22:47.701
Give us this day
our daily bread

01:22:51.053 --> 01:22:51.836
and forgive us
our trespasses

01:22:54.012 --> 01:22:57.755
as we forgive those
who trespass against us

01:22:57.798 --> 01:22:58.408
and lead us not
into temptation

01:23:00.758 --> 01:23:02.934
but deliver us from evil.

01:23:02.978 --> 01:23:03.239
Amen.

01:23:04.675 --> 01:23:06.938
Whoever you are

01:23:06.982 --> 01:23:07.156
I cast you out!

01:23:09.332 --> 01:23:11.943
Now and forever,

01:23:11.987 --> 01:23:12.291
in the name of Jesus Christ,

01:23:14.859 --> 01:23:14.902
be gone!

01:23:16.992 --> 01:23:18.863
Be gone!

01:23:23.389 --> 01:23:24.956
Be gone.

01:23:25.000 --> 01:23:27.524
[Catherine gasping]

01:23:38.100 --> 01:23:40.015
[whispering]
- Philip...

01:23:40.798 --> 01:23:42.278
Philip...

01:23:45.498 --> 01:23:47.848
Philip....

01:23:48.371 --> 01:23:50.112
Philip!

01:23:55.856 --> 01:23:57.945
[crying]
Philip...

01:24:14.527 --> 01:24:18.140
- [Father Andrew] Then there
was war in heaven...

01:24:18.270 --> 01:24:23.275
Michael and his angels
fought against the dragon.

01:24:23.319 --> 01:24:24.059
The dragon and his angels
fought back,

01:24:26.713 --> 01:24:28.976
but he was not
strong enough,

01:24:29.020 --> 01:24:32.676
and they lost their place
in heaven.

01:24:32.719 --> 01:24:33.242
The great dragon
was thrown down,

01:24:36.854 --> 01:24:37.246
that ancient serpent,

01:24:38.943 --> 01:24:39.291
who is called the Devil
and Satan,

01:24:41.859 --> 01:24:42.164
the deceiver
of the whole world.

01:24:45.515 --> 01:24:49.040
He was thrown
down to earth,

01:24:49.084 --> 01:24:49.258
and his angels
were thrown down with him.

01:24:55.873 --> 01:24:57.353
- See you downstairs?

01:24:58.223 --> 01:24:59.355
- Okay.

01:25:00.834 --> 01:25:02.097
- Hey.

01:25:09.191 --> 01:25:10.453
- I love you.

01:25:10.583 --> 01:25:12.672
- I love you, too.

01:25:16.198 --> 01:25:17.634
[Catherine chuckles]

01:25:26.686 --> 01:25:28.123
Don't be long!

01:25:28.166 --> 01:25:30.429
[dramatic music swells]

01:25:30.473 --> 01:25:32.475
♪♪

01:26:21.828 --> 01:26:23.308
[door slams shut]

01:26:25.876 --> 01:26:26.746
- Oh!

01:26:26.790 --> 01:26:28.270
- Oh, I'm so sorry!

01:26:28.313 --> 01:26:28.618
- Please,
don't worry about it!

01:26:30.446 --> 01:26:30.837
- You just moving in?

01:26:33.100 --> 01:26:36.060
- Yeah! I'm moving into
the apartment upstairs!

01:26:37.496 --> 01:26:39.237
[Sonia chuckles]

01:26:39.281 --> 01:26:39.542
I'm Sonia!

01:26:42.284 --> 01:26:43.763
- Philip.

01:26:51.118 --> 01:26:53.469
[eerie music]

01:26:53.512 --> 01:26:55.514
♪♪

01:27:00.127 --> 01:27:02.129
♪♪

01:27:50.352 --> 01:27:52.745
[light dramatic music]

01:27:52.789 --> 01:27:54.791
♪♪
